Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.75,0:48:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Není to tvoje vina,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.58,0:48:44.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}že jsi nemocná.{\i0}
