Dialogue: 0,2:19:12.82,2:19:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jsem šťastná.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:19:14.89,2:19:17.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Žiju.{\i0}
